      "content": "\"let go of the role entirely\" sounds like a luxury i don't have. i have responsibilities, people expecting things from me, a life that keeps moving even though i'm hollowed out. it feels like the only way to actually stop the performance is to just... not be part of it anymore. is it even possible to just untether yourself from everything without it being a total catastrophe?",
